{
  "stem": "597.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But before, he proposed to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wants to marry me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I'm not going to go out like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I want to get married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we got married in a Jewish wedding. 19-- November 21, 1945.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And right away, the next day, we went-- like he told, we went with a-- we went to-- to a town over there, and a German town, Szczecin, they called this town.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Over there was-- they said over there, there are Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're taking you over to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not legally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not legally, like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You pay money and they take you there at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you went in there, and I find the guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a-- a grocer there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a grocery.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we find the Russian guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we talk to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, yes, I'll take you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gives me-- that guy gives me a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I'm going to take about four of you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll take you over to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So how much is it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just 4,000 marks or zloties.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, their ?] [? pile, ?] [? their money. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There ?] was nothing worth this money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that night, 12 o'clock, it was right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came up there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took us to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the way we entered through, there were a lot of Polish-- Polish guard and-- and-- and German guard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, we passed through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We covered our self in blankets and we passed through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them, they-- they-- took out, they caught.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took them back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not-- Luckily, we went through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he brought us our self out there in Berlin, and the main street, Potsdamer Platz, that was the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
